messages.text: Hey, I'm reaching you about the part time job with www.accio.com I guess I need to share the code PEINBL06
Hello, my name is Olina. I'm glad to hear from you. What's your name?

First, I should tell you that this isn't a formal hiring opportunity, but rather my side job. I received an offer from the company to invite new people to receive commissions, so I contacted you. What I'm presenting to you is a part-time online job I'm doing. If you're interested, I'll present this job to you in writing via Telegram.
OK, then I'll send you a job profile to read.

Company Name: ACCIO.com Position: Product Data Optimizer Responsibilities: - Generate product data. - Optimize product sales ranking. Job Description: Help retailers optimize product sales and upload data to increase product exposure, presence and sales, and get better ranking in the app store. Working Hours: 10:00am to 9:00pm UK time, 1-2 hours per day. Time and location are up to you.
What skills do I need to do this job?
All you need is to be able to operate a mobile phone, and I will teach you how to do the work.
Sounds great. How can I provide the results of my work? And what be the compensation for it? Renata mentioned some training.

If you successfully complete two sets of data optimization every day, you can sign in on the working day and receive a basic salary. Work for 7 consecutive days and receive a basic salary of $500. Work for 15 consecutive days and receive a basic salary of $1,500. Work for 30 consecutive days and receive a basic salary of $2,000. You can receive a basic salary three times a month, with a total monthly basic salary of 4,000 USDT. Our remuneration is a base salary + commission. The commission is based on your workload. The principle is simple: the more you do, the more you earn. Here is our job description and salary. Please take a look at this first. If you have any questions, please feel free to ask me.
